name: XRInputSourceArray.keys
description: The keys() method in the XRInputSourceArray interface returns a JavaScript iterator which can then be used to iterate over the keys used to reference each item in the array of input sources.
content:
Secure context
This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS), in some or all supporting browsers.

Thekeys()method in the XRInputSourceArray interface returns a JavaScript iterator which can then be used to iterate over the keys used to reference each item in the array of input sources.
